      <title>MicroStrategy 正在进行股票销售以购买比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/microstrategy-makes-fourth-straight-weekly-purchase-of-bitcoin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在宣布计划通过股票销售筹集 210 亿美元以帮助资助额外购买比特币后仅一个多月，MicroStrategy Inc. 就已接近其目标的一半。]]></description>
